        <definition>uint8_t drv2605_rom_data::seq_regs[8]</definition>
        <argsstring>[8]</argsstring>
        <name>seq_regs</name>
        <qualifiedname>drv2605_rom_data::seq_regs</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Waveform sequencer contents. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This array contains the register values for the sequencer registers (0x04 to 0x0B). Each byte can describe either:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>A waveform identifier (1 to 123) from the selected library to be played.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>A wait time, if the MSB is set. The lower 7 bits are a multiple of 10 ms. Playback stops at the first zero entry.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>See Table 8 of the DRV2605 datasheet. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
        </inbodydescription>
        <location file="zephyr/drivers/haptics/drv2605.h" line="122" column="9" bodyfile="zephyr/drivers/haptics/drv2605.h" bodystart="122" bodyend="-1"/>
